des:
Use Alexa to voice control your SmartGlo products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our "one smart home" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "one smart home" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "one smart home" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on [device name]"
"Alexa, turn off [device name]" 
"Alexa, set the [device name] brightness to (10%, 25%, 50%, 75% and 100%)"
"Alexa, set the [device name] colour to (Red, orange, yellow, green, blue, purple or pink)"
